{"tid":2489447,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【三年內第二單】利物浦球迷擲毁皇馬隊巴 警方調查事件","createTime":"2021-04-15T03:07:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-15T03:18:10.000Z","uid":165817,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c9323192635fcd81bc2a5882bde58876eb3b5968","tid":2489447,"uid":165817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T03:07:41.000Z","msg":"　　歐聯八強次回合，作客利物浦的皇家馬德里球員坐巴士前往晏菲路途中，有巴士玻璃被人投擲物件擊毀。<br />\n<br />\n　　利物浦發表聲明，譴責球迷的行為「可恥」及「完全不能接受」，向皇家馬德里誠摯道歉，強調會配合警方調查事件。<br />\n<br />\n　　這並非利物浦球迷首次破壞敵軍隊巴。三年前歐聯八強，利物浦球迷向對手曼城的巴士投擲煙霧彈、啤酒瓶和汽水罐等雜物，大巴的玻璃窗毀爛。<br />\n<br />\n　　利物浦當時事後向曼城道歉，指會方已經用盡一切辦法防止事件發生，球會亦予以譴責，同樣批評相關行為「完全不能接受」。<br />\n<br />\n　　皇家馬德里最終以總比數三比一淘汰利物浦，晉身四強。"},{"pid":"ea43043c50ed3aa0ede202ab6a8d578086d8c462","tid":2489447,"uid":50385,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T03:12:02.000Z","msg":"Dirty work 總要有人做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e77e911fe0ec0d8cb36cf4cf72e5bf631a37bba8","tid":2489447,"uid":33730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T03:13:33.000Z","msg":"破大巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be450838a39358c998c9e93600309ae415c5afe9","tid":2489447,"uid":238920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T03:14:55.000Z","msg":"一定係拉莫斯造成<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abe87af1ee8e1bb54d67237c5ee020008994d414","tid":2489447,"uid":59283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T03:14:57.000Z","msg":"摩連奴殺手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e39ea12375b628f764b942667b75bc19d66845f","tid":2489447,"uid":165817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ea43043c50ed3aa0ede202ab6a8d578086d8c462","tid":2489447,"uid":50385,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T03:12:02.000Z","msg":